Class ExecuteStrategiesCommand

    • de.upb.crc901.proseco.command.ExecuteStrategiesCommand

    Command

    public class ExecuteStrategiesCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements Command
    ExecuteStrategiesCommand, searches for strategy subfolders and forking a new process for each strategy. Output and Error streams of these processes are directed to systemlog/systemOut.log and systemlog/systemErr.log files respectively.
